{"tid":524840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【反metoo】嘉芙蓮丹露等百位歐洲女性發公開信“捍衛求歡的自由”","createTime":"2018-01-10T04:28:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T06:06:32.000Z","uid":48479,"like":461,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"ebd8de8821b0ec2fe1808cdf6f8d2710c05dc908","tid":524840,"uid":48479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T04:28:17.000Z","msg":"曾經主演《8美千嬌》《青樓紅杏》的法國著名女演員嘉芙蓮&middot;丹露與包括她在內的100位歐洲知名女性表達對荷里活正在如火如荼展開的反對性騷擾運動的不同觀點，她們認為男性應該&ldquo;自由的接觸&rdquo;（free to hit on）女性，而像&ldquo;Metoo&rdquo;等反擊性騷擾的運動可能會矯枉過正。<br />\n<br />\n      在當地時間星期二發表的《法國世界報》上，包括丹露在內的100位社會各個領域歐洲知名女性發表了一封共同簽署了公開信，警示荷里活反對性騷擾的活動正在引發一場新&ldquo;清教主義&rdquo;（puritanism）的盛行。<br />\n<br />\n      信中指出這一波&ldquo;淨化&rdquo;浪潮似乎並沒有任何界限，因為有人開始審查海報上的埃貢&middot;席勒（Egon Schiele）的裸體畫作，有人被要求取消波蘭斯基（Roman Polanski）的舊作回顧。甚至有人認為安東尼奧尼（Michelangelo Antonioni）的《春光乍洩》（Blowup）是&ldquo;厭惡女性&rdquo;和&ldquo;令人難以接受&rdquo;的。<br />\n<br />\n      同時她們還認為Metoo活動已經導致了&ldquo;對一些人的公開指控，而他們甚至沒有回應和辯護的可能，就被完全等同於性犯罪者。男性被草率的懲罰了，只是因為他們想碰觸某人的膝蓋，或者試圖偷一個吻就被迫失去了工作。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n      信中稱&ldquo;強姦是犯罪，但持續而笨拙的試圖誘惑某人，男人們這種紳士的沙文主義攻擊並不是犯罪。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n      她們表示公開反對一些男性的濫用職權是合理並必須的，但不斷的譴責已經失去了控制。同時她們認為，這種做法將促成一種公眾情緒，女性被視作軟弱無力的永久的受害者。<br />\n<br />\n      信中還寫道：&ldquo;作為女性，我們不認可這樣的女權主義，這除了譴責權力濫用，還體現了對男性和性的憎恨。&rdquo;而她們堅持&ldquo;捍衛人們求歡(importune)的自由，這是性自由所必不可少的。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/film/2018/jan/09/catherine-deneuve-men-should-be-free-hit-on-women-harvey-weinstein-scandal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ffilm%2F2018%2Fjan%2F09%2Fcatherine-deneuve-men-should-be-free-hit-on-women-harvey-weinstein-scandal&d=jv5VVIV7ClBSI%2BGCvZSj9cVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=80bf15ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/film/2018/jan/09/catherine-deneuve-men-should-be-free-hit-on-women-harvey-weinstein-scandal</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mtime.com/2018/01/10/1577187.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mtime.com%2F2018%2F01%2F10%2F1577187.html&d=jv5VVIV7ClBSI%2BGCvZSj9cVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=3f6eca97\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mtime.com/2018/01/10/1577187.html</a>"},{"pid":"b5d1982f626d2d36fdff33f8bc0ebb14c0b4b4e5","tid":524840,"uid":40216,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T04:35:56.000Z","msg":"法國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66e0e5a6379d66919d19076ffd68de85b082d447","tid":524840,"uid":37933,"like":118,"dislike":1,"score":117,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T04:38:03.000Z","msg":"理性女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2f025fcdcc9af92397bc46a0f77e0567891e007","tid":524840,"uid":132859,"like":100,"dislike":2,"score":98,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T04:39:03.000Z","msg":"法國妹咪心水清咯<br />\n班婦權左膠乜都上綱上線到去侵犯身體自主權<br />\n但明明佢地要嘅野係現實冇可能存在<br />\n都格硬要去做<br />\n搞到大家驚到正常社交都唔敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48dfeb507280ba3f0301b16c47f0dcddc7d0aedc","tid":524840,"uid":26752,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T04:41:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>@ 柴田ミチコ</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"e3201afd8429ee81cfa2af24941bf54a7f4825b5","tid":524840,"uid":26752,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"f2f025fcdcc9af92397bc46a0f77e0567891e007","tid":524840,"uid":132859,"like":100,"dislike":2,"score":98,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T04:39:03.000Z","msg":"法國妹咪心水清咯<br />\n班婦權左膠乜都上綱上線到去侵犯身體自主權<br />\n但明明佢地要嘅野係現實冇可能存在<br />\n都格硬要去做<br />\n搞到大家驚到正常社交都唔敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T04:42:21.000Z","msg":"唔比物化女人<br />\n但做雞物化自己就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c35aed07aada93a3913218f20f79de981cba8cd","tid":524840,"uid":11512,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"48dfeb507280ba3f0